ai, a hanga ana e ahau he whare mo te ingoa o Ihowa, o te Atua o Ih
araira.

<span id="an_6:11">6:11</span> Na kua whakatakotoria e ahau ki reira te
aaka, kei roto nei ta Ihowa kawenata, i whakaritea e ia ki nga tama a
Iharaira.

<span id="an_6:12">6:12</span> ¶ Na ka tu ia ki mua i te aata a Ihowa, i
