whakaminenga katoa o Iharaira, wherahia ana ona ringa whaka te rangi:

<span id="an_6:14">6:14</span> Na ka mea ia, E Ihowa, e te Atua o
Iharaira, kahore he Atua hei rite mou i te rangi, i te whenua; e pupuri
nei i te kawenata, i te aroha ki au pononga, ina whakapaua o ratou
