<span id="an_8:11">8:11</span> I kawea atu hoki e Horomona te tamahine a
Parao i te pa o Rawiri ki te whare i hanga e ia mona. I mea hoki ia,
Kaua taku wahine e noho ki te whare o Rawiri kingi o Iharaira; he tapu
