<span id="an_18:13">18:13</span> Na ka mea a Mikaia, E ora ana a Ihowa,
ina, ko ta toku Atua e korero mai ai ki ahau, ko taku tena e korero ai.

<span id="an_18:14">18:14</span> A, no tona taenga ki te kingi, ka mea
te kingi ki a ia, E Mikaia, me haere ranei matou ki Ramoto Kireara ki te
