<span id="an_18:24">18:24</span> Ano ra ko Mikaia, Tera koe e kite i te
ra e haere ai koe ki tetahi ruma i roto rawa piri ai.

<span id="an_18:25">18:25</span> Katahi te kingi o Iharaira ka mea,
Kawea atu a Mikaia, whakahokia ki a Amono rangatira o te pa, ki a Ioaha
