<span id="an_18:28">18:28</span> ¶ Heoi haere ana te kingi o Iharaira
raua ko Iehohapata, kingi o Hura ki runga, ki Ramoto Kireara.

<span id="an_18:29">18:29</span> Na ka mea te kingi o Iharaira ki a
