<span id="an_24:15">24:15</span> ¶ Otiia kua koroheketia a Iehoiara, kua
maha ona ra, a ka mate: kotahi rau e toru tekau ona tau i tona matenga.

<span id="an_24:16">24:16</span> A tanumia ana ia ki te pa o Rawiri ki
