ke. Kua whakarerea nei e koutou a Ihowa na kua whakarerea hoki koutou e
ia.

<span id="an_24:21">24:21</span> Na ka whakatupuria e ratou he he mona,
a akina ia ki te kohatu, na te kingi i whakahau, ki te marae o te whare
